snippet.title: BANJO KAZOOIE X DONKEY KONG COUNTRY - (Custom Mod)
snippet.description:
#banjokazooie #donkeykong #nintendo64 
Crossover between two of RARE's most emblematic games. The mod includes only one playable level (Jungle Hijinx) and it is already finished.

DOWNLOAD:
Drop your "Banjo-Kazooie (U) [!].z64" rom here:  
https://patch.wedarobi.com/bk_jungle_hijinx

SOUNDTRACK:
https://mega.nz/#!4pNHhSjJ!4cOC3svX3QRESvXrNK7YRX-Rkq1nwVwqZYetqUyJHEM
